title: Match of the Day - 18th April 2015 - hdtv x264

SPORT: Match of the Day
On: BBC 1 HD     
Date: Saturday 18th April 2015 
Time: 22:30 to 23:40 

Gabby Logan introduces highlights of the day's five Premier League matches, including title-chasing Chelsea against Manchester United, Everton's home game with Burnley and relegation-threatened Leicester versus Swansea. Meanwhile, Stoke welcome Southampton and Crystal Palace meet West Brom.
The studio experts are the B team: Phil Neville & Robbie Savage :(
